unable to support two kids.

23
00:01:46,548 --> 00:01:47,228
Then he's really

24
00:01:47,308 --> 00:01:48,708
shooting himself in the foot.

25
00:01:48,908 --> 00:01:50,507
Since he won't stop,

26
00:01:50,708 --> 00:01:52,068
then we won't be polite either.

27
00:01:52,468 --> 00:01:53,468
What do you want to do?

28
00:01:54,227 --> 00:01:55,227
Sue him.

29
00:01:55,548 --> 00:01:57,748
Redistribute marital assets.

30
00:01:57,908 --> 00:01:59,828
This stingy rooster, Qian Hao,

31
00:01:59,988 --> 00:02:01,628
I'll pluck his feathers one by one

32
00:02:01,708 --> 00:02:03,387
from him.

33
00:02:03,748 --> 00:02:04,707
What's going on?

34
00:02:04,787 --> 00:02:07,108
How did it become 2.7 yuan?

35
00:02:07,188 --> 00:02:07,868
Why stare at me?

36
00:02:07,948 --> 00:02:08,988
I didn't monitor it.

37
00:02:09,068 --> 00:02:09,829
The backend is...

38
00:02:09,909 --> 00:02:11,068
Who put up the link? Yao?

39
00:02:11,068 --> 00:02:12,387
Yao, you were monitoring the backend.

40
00:02:12,387 --> 00:02:14,307
Yes, but I locked the orders promptly.

41
00:02:14,387 --> 00:02:15,068
Why?

42
00:02:15,148 --> 00:02:16,028
Locked to this price?

43
00:02:16,108 --> 00:02:17,068
Ten thousand orders!

44
00:02:17,148 --> 00:02:17,829
What's the cost?

45
00:02:17,909 --> 00:02:19,468
Alright, stop arguing.

46
00:02:19,628 --> 00:02:20,587
What's the point?

47
00:02:20,667 --> 00:02:21,828
Think of a solution.

48
00:02:21,908 --> 00:02:22,948
How to solve this price?

49
00:02:23,028 --> 00:02:24,312
Cheaper than wholesale price.

50
00:02:24,707 --> 00:02:25,828
Quickly call Mei.

51
00:02:25,908 --> 00:02:26,427
Let me.

52
00:02:26,507 --> 00:02:27,348
Tell him to come.

53
00:02:27,428 --> 00:02:28,428
Get him back.

54
00:02:28,588 --> 00:02:29,348
What's going on?

55
00:02:29,428 --> 00:02:30,428
Hurry up.

56
00:02:33,580 --> 00:02:35,256
(Incoming call, Yao.
Answer, Reject)

57
00:02:38,227 --> 00:02:39,147
Hello, what's up?

58
00:02:39,227 --> 00:02:40,587
Mei, where are you now?

59
00:02:40,667 --> 00:02:41,947
The project has a problem.

60
00:02:42,507 --> 00:02:44,188
I'm almost there, just a bit of traffic.

61
00:02:44,547 --> 00:02:45,747
The livestream link

62
00:02:45,827 --> 00:02:46,627
