63
00:02:46,627 --> 00:02:47,708
It's supposed to be 27 yuan.

64
00:02:47,708 --> 00:02:48,948
But now it's 2.7 yuan.

65
00:02:49,028 --> 00:02:50,987
Over 10,000 orders have been placed.

66
00:03:00,908 --> 00:03:02,348
Mei, what happened?

67
00:03:02,468 --> 00:03:03,787
Nothing. Let's go upstairs.

68
00:03:04,588 --> 00:03:05,188
- Rest assured.
- We'll...

69
00:03:05,268 --> 00:03:07,188
- We'll come up with a solution today.
- Confirm the issue again.

70
00:03:07,268 --> 00:03:08,827
Mei, you're finally here.

71
00:03:09,588 --> 00:03:10,508
Alright, don't worry.

72
00:03:10,588 --> 00:03:11,348
Mei, you're back.

73
00:03:11,428 --> 00:03:12,427
What exactly is going on?

74
00:03:12,507 --> 00:03:13,188
Mr. Chen blames

75
00:03:13,268 --> 00:03:14,548
our new assistant broadcaster's

76
00:03:14,548 --> 00:03:16,188
unclear communication with the platform.

77
00:03:16,188 --> 00:03:17,508
The product was originally 40.

78
00:03:17,588 --> 00:03:18,268
Livestream price

79
00:03:18,348 --> 00:03:19,348
should have been 27.

80
00:03:19,547 --> 00:03:20,548
Now suddenly, somehow...

81
00:03:20,628 --> 00:03:22,428
- It has suddenly dropped to 2.7.
- Yes.

82
00:03:22,508 --> 00:03:23,508
All the fans went crazy.

83
00:03:23,588 --> 00:03:24,308
In one minute,

84
00:03:24,388 --> 00:03:25,427
10,000 orders were placed.

85
00:03:25,507 --> 00:03:27,192
When we realized it
and locked the orders,

86
00:03:27,192 --> 00:03:28,856
over 300,000 yuan had been lost.

87
00:03:29,707 --> 00:03:30,308
But...

88
00:03:30,388 --> 00:03:31,747
Have they given an explanation?

89
00:03:31,827 --> 00:03:32,387
Yes.

90
00:03:32,628 --> 00:03:34,187
But they only agree to cover half.

91
00:03:34,267 --> 00:03:35,508
They said when the link was up,

92
00:03:35,588 --> 00:03:36,508
we didn't notice

93
00:03:36,588 --> 00:03:37,188
immediately.

94
00:03:37,268 --> 00:03:38,588
We share some responsibility.

95
00:03:39,348 --> 00:03:39,949
Alright.

96
00:03:40,029 --> 00:03:41,307
I'll contact the manufacturer.

97
00:03:41,387 --> 00:03:42,588
No need, Mei.

98
00:03:42,748 --> 00:03:43,429
The manufacturer

99
00:03:43,429 --> 00:03:44,627
is surely overjoyed.

100
00:03:44,707 --> 00:03:46,188
Someone covers the price difference.

101
00:03:46,188 --> 00:03:47,069
And they got high sales

102
00:03:47,069 --> 00:03:48,027
and gained advertising.

103
00:03:48,107 --> 00:03:49,107
Exactly.

104
00:03:49,748 --> 00:03:50,748
Mei Chengyi,

105
00:03:51,267 --> 00:03:52,348
come to my office.

106
00:03:55,387 --> 00:03:56,787
What should we do, Mei?

107
00:03:59,707 --> 00:04:00,428
Alright.

108
00:04:00,508 --> 00:04:01,787
I'll handle that old fellow.

109
00:04:02,428 --> 00:04:03,428
Do you need me to come?

110
00:04:03,787 --> 00:04:04,787
