No eggs, either.

112
00:04:07,308 --> 00:04:08,588
I'll order some in a while.

113
00:04:08,827 --> 00:04:09,387
Don't.

114
00:04:09,827 --> 00:04:11,108
I'll just go to the market.

115
00:04:11,188 --> 00:04:12,307
It's fresh and cheap.

116
00:04:12,387 --> 00:04:13,107
Mr. You.

117
00:04:13,387 --> 00:04:14,148
Grocery shopping.

118
00:04:14,228 --> 00:04:16,267
That's a misconception
of your old ideas.

119
00:04:16,347 --> 00:04:17,307
Foods sold on the apps

120
00:04:17,387 --> 00:04:18,427
are fresh and convenient.

121
00:04:18,507 --> 00:04:19,788
It can also save time.

122
00:04:19,947 --> 00:04:20,628
If any issues,

123
00:04:20,708 --> 00:04:21,827
you can contact them.

124
00:04:22,668 --> 00:04:23,788
Save time?

125
00:04:25,347 --> 00:04:26,347
For what?

126
00:04:26,587 --> 00:04:27,587
Games?

127
00:04:28,267 --> 00:04:29,548
As if your time

128
00:04:29,628 --> 00:04:30,868
is so valuable.

129
00:04:31,308 --> 00:04:32,467
I mean...

130
00:04:32,748 --> 00:04:34,348
Youyou, you drive.

131
00:04:34,428 --> 00:04:35,587
You come shopping with me.

132
00:04:35,748 --> 00:04:38,068
Just think of it as
spending some casual time with me.

133
00:04:38,228 --> 00:04:40,068
You're the customer
and you have the final say.

134
00:04:41,467 --> 00:04:42,467
You...

135
00:04:44,628 --> 00:04:46,147
Why are you stepping on my foot?

136
00:04:56,907 --> 00:04:57,907
Smells good.

137
00:04:58,707 --> 00:04:59,707
Then buy one of these.

138
00:04:59,827 --> 00:05:00,827
Here to buy groceries?

139
00:05:02,108 --> 00:05:03,108
You too?

140
00:05:03,907 --> 00:05:05,187
Isn't this Youyou?

141
00:05:05,267 --> 00:05:06,267
Didn't go to work?

142
00:05:06,347 --> 00:05:07,947
Accompany your mom here?

143
00:05:08,147 --> 00:05:08,668
Hi, auntie.

144
00:05:08,748 --> 00:05:09,748
Youyou is beautiful.

145
00:05:09,868 --> 00:05:11,507
Back in the country, still adjusting.

146
00:05:11,587 --> 00:05:12,708
I let her stay at home

147
00:05:12,788 --> 00:05:14,027
to spend more time with me.

148
00:05:14,467 --> 00:05:15,947
I'm going over there to buy meat.

149
00:05:16,027 --> 00:05:17,148
- Alright
- Talk later.

150
00:05:17,228 --> 00:05:18,108
- Alright.
- Go ahead.

151
00:05:18,188 --> 00:05:19,188
Goodbye.

152
00:05:22,308 --> 00:05:23,109
Let me tell you.

153
00:05:23,189 --> 00:05:24,747
It's a pity for Mr. You's family.

154
00:05:24,827 --> 00:05:25,947
The eldest daughter

155
00:05:26,027 --> 00:05:27,747
was both capable and sensible.

156
00:05:27,827 --> 00:05:29,307
She fell ill and died early.

157
00:05:29,387 --> 00:05:30,348
They spent lots of money

158
00:05:30,348 --> 00:05:31,747
