159
00:05:31,827 --> 00:05:32,588
to send her abroad

160
00:05:32,588 --> 00:05:33,867
for a mediocre university.

161
00:05:33,947 --> 00:05:34,828
It's of no use at all.

162
00:05:34,908 --> 00:05:36,228
Now she is staying at home.

163
00:05:36,748 --> 00:05:37,508
When

164
00:05:37,588 --> 00:05:38,627
playing chess downstairs,

165
00:05:38,707 --> 00:05:40,347
Mr. You always complained to others.

166
00:05:40,947 --> 00:05:41,628
So young.

167
00:05:41,708 --> 00:05:42,988
Living off parents at home.

168
00:05:43,068 --> 00:05:44,588
Wasn't studying in vain?

169
00:05:44,668 --> 00:05:45,267
Do you know?

170
00:05:45,347 --> 00:05:45,868
Now many

171
00:05:45,948 --> 00:05:47,028
young people

172
00:05:47,108 --> 00:05:48,067
