173
00:05:48,147 --> 00:05:49,147
What do you want to eat?

174
00:05:52,068 --> 00:05:53,068
Let me try it.

175
00:05:55,988 --> 00:05:56,708
That one.

176
00:05:56,788 --> 00:05:57,788
Okay.

177
00:06:00,467 --> 00:06:00,989
Don't tell me

178
00:06:01,069 --> 00:06:02,387
