so many proposals.

180
00:06:04,428 --> 00:06:06,028
The company trusts you.

181
00:06:06,108 --> 00:06:08,028
I have the thought
of wanting to help you.

182
00:06:08,108 --> 00:06:09,067
Such an important proposal

183
00:06:09,147 --> 00:06:10,147
was handed over to you.

184
00:06:10,267 --> 00:06:11,627
Your chosen partner erred.

185
00:06:11,707 --> 00:06:12,708
It's your mistake.

186
00:06:12,788 --> 00:06:13,788
Understand?

187
00:06:14,228 --> 00:06:15,387
I understand, Ms. Li.

188
00:06:15,868 --> 00:06:17,387
I won't shirk responsibility.

189
00:06:17,707 --> 00:06:18,628
But now I think

190
00:06:18,708 --> 00:06:20,428
it's not the time
to pursue responsibility.

191
00:06:20,827 --> 00:06:21,589
I'll have the team

192
00:06:21,669 --> 00:06:22,867
come up with a PR plan quick

193
00:06:22,947 --> 00:06:24,387
and a plan to recover losses.

194
00:06:24,467 --> 00:06:25,347
Is that okay?

195
00:06:25,467 --> 00:06:26,627
Later,

196
00:06:26,707 --> 00:06:28,788
