or pursue accountability.

197
00:06:28,868 --> 00:06:29,868
What do you say?

198
00:06:30,507 --> 00:06:32,308
Now there's a problem with one client.

199
00:06:33,068 --> 00:06:33,948
Then aren't other

200
00:06:34,028 --> 00:06:35,068
clients afraid?

201
00:06:36,548 --> 00:06:37,548
Let me tell you.

202
00:06:37,668 --> 00:06:38,668
I only give you one day

203
00:06:38,748 --> 00:06:39,467
to solve this.

204
00:06:39,748 --> 00:06:40,988
For all subsequent losses,

205
00:06:41,068 --> 00:06:42,228
the company isn't liable.

206
00:06:42,308 --> 00:06:43,308
Keep that in mind.

207
00:06:44,228 --> 00:06:45,267
If not handled well,

208
00:06:45,428 --> 00:06:47,147
I can't protect you this time.

209
00:06:50,068 --> 00:06:51,068
I know, Ms. Li.

210
00:06:52,068 --> 00:06:53,068
Thank you, Ms. Li.

211
00:07:01,907 --> 00:07:02,907
Mom.

212
00:07:04,827 --> 00:07:06,707
Hello, I'll have this piece.

213
00:07:07,188 --> 00:07:08,188
Chop it finer.

214
00:07:10,147 --> 00:07:11,147
Angry?

215
00:07:13,147 --> 00:07:14,387
What I mean is,

216
00:07:14,668 --> 00:07:15,827
after Xu left,

217
00:07:15,988 --> 00:07:17,427
we notice you have

218
00:07:17,507 --> 00:07:18,668
some emotions to Mei Chengyi.

219
00:07:19,068 --> 00:07:20,788
We have also reflected a bit.

220
00:07:20,947 --> 00:07:22,827
Did we overlook your feelings?

221
00:07:23,827 --> 00:07:25,187
We've been discussing it for ages.

222
00:07:25,267 --> 00:07:26,468
Keep the best in the family.

223
00:07:26,548 --> 00:07:28,788
We've always wanted to match you two up.

224
00:07:29,068 --> 00:07:30,068
But who would've thought

225
00:07:30,228 --> 00:07:31,307
that Xu

226
00:07:31,387 --> 00:07:32,427
would suddenly appear.

227
00:07:32,507 --> 00:07:33,507
Though,

228
00:07:33,827 --> 00:07:35,028
we think she's nice,

229
00:07:35,108 --> 00:07:37,027
but we definitely support you.

230
00:07:37,147 --> 00:07:38,348
As long as you're happy,

231
00:07:38,428 --> 00:07:39,029
then we can

232
00:07:39,109 --> 00:07:40,507
break up any couple.

233
00:07:40,827 --> 00:07:42,027
Mom, I was wrong.

234
00:07:42,147 --> 00:07:42,788
I was wrong.

235
00:07:42,868 --> 00:07:43,428
I don't like

236
00:07:43,508 --> 00:07:45,387
Chengyi at all.

237
00:07:46,027 --> 00:07:46,709
I'm angry

238
00:07:46,789 --> 00:07:47,908
because I feel Mei Chengyi

239
00:07:47,988 --> 00:07:48,988
is lying.

240
00:07:49,628 --> 00:07:50,908
He seemed so set

241
00:07:50,988 --> 00:07:51,668
on mourning

242
00:07:51,668 --> 00:07:52,507
my sister forever,

243
00:07:52,507 --> 00:07:53,109
that I wanted to

244
00:07:53,109 --> 00:07:54,264
give him a chastity arch.

245
00:07:54,668 --> 00:07:56,428
He even said Xu Kaixin is just...

246
00:07:57,027 --> 00:07:58,027
Just what?

247
00:07:58,188 --> 00:07:59,747
It's done, 68.

248
00:07:59,827 --> 00:08:00,827
68.

249
00:08:01,188 --> 00:08:02,188
Okay.

250
00:08:02,587 --> 00:08:03,788
Just playing.

251
00:08:04,347 --> 00:08:05,348
And now look,

252
00:08:05,428 --> 00:08:06,707
they've quickly gotten together.

253
00:08:06,868 --> 00:08:08,308
I just feel pity for my sister.

254
00:08:09,548 --> 00:08:10,427
I know

255
00:08:10,507 --> 00:08:11,507
he has to move on.

256
00:08:11,988 --> 00:08:12,988
But knowing and seeing it

257
00:08:13,068 --> 00:08:14,387
are two different things.

258
00:08:16,548 --> 00:08:18,267
When you were with street boys,

259
00:08:18,428 --> 00:08:19,109
we've seen you

260
00:08:19,189 --> 00:08:20,788
kissing and hugging many times.

261
00:08:20,947 --> 00:08:21,628
Now you let

262
00:08:21,708 --> 00:08:22,947
a man in his thirties engage in

263
00:08:23,027 --> 00:08:24,387
a spiritual relationship?

264
00:08:25,188 --> 00:08:26,228
Don't mention street boys.

265
00:08:26,308 --> 00:08:27,507
Mom, I'm sorry.

266
00:08:30,228 --> 00:08:30,988
Let me take it.

267
00:08:31,068 --> 00:08:32,068
Let me take it.

268
00:08:33,308 --> 00:08:35,227
Go, go, go. Let's go.

269
00:08:36,068 --> 00:08:37,308
Seriously.

270
00:08:41,227 --> 00:08:41,949
Ms. Xu,

271
00:08:42,029 --> 00:08:43,388
