272
00:08:43,388 --> 00:08:44,309
And now you remembered

273
00:08:44,389 --> 00:08:46,428
to pursue the re-division
of divorce assets?

274
00:08:47,148 --> 00:08:48,708
In these three years,

275
00:08:48,788 --> 00:08:50,387
my ex-husband has never contacted me.

276
00:08:50,467 --> 00:08:51,308
But recently,

277
00:08:51,467 --> 00:08:52,547
their whole family

278
00:08:52,627 --> 00:08:53,188
wants to get

279
00:08:53,268 --> 00:08:54,189
the custody of my son.

280
00:08:54,269 --> 00:08:55,908
They often make their presence known.

281
00:08:56,347 --> 00:08:58,107
