done many despicable things.

282
00:08:58,308 --> 00:08:59,667
Since they won't stop,

283
00:08:59,747 --> 00:09:00,469
then let it be so.

284
00:09:00,549 --> 00:09:02,028
Yes, take the initiative.

285
00:09:02,188 --> 00:09:03,907
They're addicted
to bullying good people.

286
00:09:03,987 --> 00:09:04,788
Moreover, Kaixin

287
00:09:04,868 --> 00:09:06,227
