1170
00:42:23,068 --> 00:42:24,268
On the other hand,

1171
00:42:24,348 --> 00:42:25,428
I'm not a saint.

1172
00:42:25,508 --> 00:42:26,228
I'm not some kind

1173
00:42:26,308 --> 00:42:27,787
of idol drama male protagonist.

1174
00:42:28,747 --> 00:42:30,227
I'm just an ordinary,

1175
00:42:30,307 --> 00:42:31,508
middle-aged man.

1176
00:42:32,707 --> 00:42:33,468
How could I live in

1177
00:42:33,548 --> 00:42:34,787
widowerhood for a lifetime?

1178
00:42:35,348 --> 00:42:37,067
No, if you...

1179
00:42:37,147 --> 00:42:38,187
Help!

1180
00:42:38,548 --> 00:42:39,509
Someone jumped into the river.

1181
00:42:39,509 --> 00:42:40,948
Hurry, help!

1182
00:42:47,627 --> 00:42:48,627
I can't swim.

1183
00:42:48,868 --> 00:42:50,107
I'm afraid to go in.

1184
00:42:50,587 --> 00:42:51,349
Help!

1185
00:42:51,429 --> 00:42:52,507
Did anyone call the police?

1186
00:42:52,587 --> 00:42:53,869
- Go down there.
- Find a pole.

1187
00:42:53,949 --> 00:42:55,307
Pull him up.

1188
00:42:55,627 --> 00:42:56,908
I'll call.

1189
00:42:56,988 --> 00:42:58,067
- Well...
- Save him.

1190
00:42:58,147 --> 00:42:59,147
Dad.

1191
00:43:26,043 --> 00:43:32,498
