1201
00:44:41,409 --> 00:44:49,117
♪Looking left and right throughout time♪

1202
00:44:49,505 --> 00:44:55,308
♪I luckily turned the tide
when I met you♪

1203
00:44:55,945 --> 00:45:03,143
♪If youthful courage
